column3: ACK, but please either verify that Armory is actually incompatible, or just remove that mention.\n
A quick look on the forum (https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=903973.0) suggests that the next Armory release will be compatible with 0.10.0\n
Did anyone actually confirm that Armory isn't compatible with this?\n
I didn't, but I thought someone said they knew it wasn't... I guess it will be soon enough, so maybe we should leave out the parenthical region?\n
I would drop the "officially" -- it's not unofficially supported either. Just a possibility of working.\n
